00:16:51,460 --> 00:16:53,210
can be cute.
很可爱的

335
00:16:54,440 --> 00:16:59,730
And someday, he's gonna make the best uncle in the world.
将来 他一定是世上最好的叔叔

336
00:16:59,740 --> 00:17:01,510
Because this Barney...
因为这个Barney...

337
00:17:01,540 --> 00:17:03,690
He's family to us.
是我们的亲人

338
00:17:14,170 --> 00:17:15,870
Excuse me.
抱歉

339
00:17:15,900 --> 00:17:18,090
I heard you're from Estonia.
我听说你是爱沙尼亚来的

340
00:17:18,110 --> 00:17:19,840
So am I.
我也是

341
00:17:19,870 --> 00:17:21,950
Excuse me one moment.
等我一下

342
00:17:24,390 --> 00:17:26,720
Estonia would close out the Baltics!
有了爱沙尼亚 波罗的海地区就全搞定了!

343
00:17:27,670 --> 00:17:32,130
And I am street performer like you.
我跟你一样是个街头艺人

344
00:17:51,140 --> 00:17:52,580
Hey.
嘿

345
00:17:52,610 --> 00:17:54,690
Say yes to this.
你必须答应我

346
00:17:54,720 --> 00:17:56,030
Okay.
好的

347
00:17:56,060 --> 00:17:58,240
Can I move back in?
我能搬回来住吗?

348
00:18:02,420 --> 00:18:04,280
Yes.
好的

349
00:18:05,880 --> 00:18:09,440
But,Ted,am I just the biggest idiot in the world?
Ted 我是不是这世上最傻的人?

350
00:18:09,480 --> 00:18:14,520
Look,think about all of us five years ago when we first met you.
想想看5年前刚认识你的时候 我们是什么情况

351
00:18:14,550 --> 00:18:16,960
Marshall and Lily were just boyfriend and girlfriend.
Marshall和Lily还是男女朋友

352
00:18:17,000 --> 00:18:19,530
Now they're married and thinking about kids.
现在他们已经结婚了 准备要孩子

353
00:18:19,570 --> 00:18:24,180
And Barney? Barney was never gonna commit to anyone ever.
Barney呢? Barney从来没对谁动过真心

354
00:18:24,210 --> 00:18:27,070
And last year,he fell in love.
去年 他恋爱了

355
00:18:27,110 --> 00:18:29,100
And me?
至于我?

356
00:18:29,130 --> 00:18:33,460
I was chasing some girl I was convinced was "The One.
我在追求一个女孩 我的"真命天女"

357
00:18:33,500 --> 00:18:36,200
" Now she's one of my closest friends.
现在她是我最要好的朋友

358
00:18:36,230 --> 00:18:37,560
And you?
而你呢?

359
00:18:37,590 --> 00:18:41,300
Five years ago,you never would have chosen love over your career,
5年前 你绝对不会选择爱情 放弃事业

360
00:18:41,330 --> 00:18:44,350
but today you did.
但现在你这么做了

361
00:18:44,380 --> 00:18:45,650
Looks like I'm getting dumber.
感觉我越来越笨了

362
00:18:45,680 --> 00:18:48,600
No, just more courageous.
不 是越来越勇敢了

363
00:18:51,350 --> 00:18:54,660
Look,we've all been searching for The Five Doppelgangers, right?
我们一直在找第五个翻版 对吗?

364
00:18:54,700 --> 00:18:57,550
But eventually,over time,
结果找了这么久

365
00:18:57,580 --> 00:19:00,430
we all become our own doppelgangers. You know,these...
我们的翻版就是自己 那些...

366
00:19:00,470 --> 00:19:05,390
these completely different people who just happen to look like us.
那些人跟我们完全不相干 只是恰好跟我们长得很像

367
00:19:06,500 --> 00:19:07,800
"Five Years Ago Robin"?
"5年前的Robin"?

368
00:19:07,850 --> 00:19:11,400
That girl,she was pretty great.
那个姑娘 非常棒

369
00:19:11,430 --> 00:19:14,920
But Doppelganger Robin?
但Robin的翻版?

370
00:19:15,450 --> 00:19:17,850
She's amazing.
是完美的

371
00:19:27,590 --> 00:19:30,840
We've,um,we've had a lot to drink...
我们... 我们还有不少酒...

372
00:19:30,880 --> 00:19:32,900
I don't care.
我不在乎

373
00:19:36,500 --> 00:19:38,000
What?
什么?

374
00:19:38,020 --> 00:19:40,900
Oh. Oh,yeah.
噢 对哦

375
00:19:40,930 --> 00:19:42,590
I forgot I'm blond.
我忘了 毛染黄了

376
00:19:42,620 --> 00:19:44,260
I have blond hair.
我是金毛狮王

377
00:19:44,800 --> 00:19:47,300
And that's the story of how dying my hair blond
这就是我的染发故事

378
00:19:47,350 --> 00:19:50,720
kept us from doing something we both would have regretted that night.
阻止我们那天晚上 做将来会后悔的事情

379
00:19:51,270 --> 00:19:54,040
Kids,the universe is funny.
孩子们 主很有意思

380
00:19:53,740 --> 00:19:55,810
{\a6}four months later...
4个月以后...

381
00:20:02,810 --> 00:20:04,710
Oh,my God!
我的老天!

382
00:20:04,760 --> 00:20:06,020
Yes!
太好了!

383
00:20:06,050 --> 00:20:07,040
You're here!
你在这儿!

384
00:20:07,070 --> 00:20:08,400
This is fantastic!
太赞了!

385
00:20:08,440 --> 00:20:09,950
Baby,simmer. Your husband's right there.
宝贝 悠着点 你的老公就在边上

386
00:20:09,990 --> 00:20:10,920
At least attempt to hide it.
至少装个矜持的样子

387
00:20:10,960 --> 00:20:13,420
Guys,follow me!
伙计们 跟我过来!

388
00:20:16,280 --> 00:20:18,150
Guys,look!
你们看!

389
00:20:18,180 --> 00:20:20,650
The Fifth Doppelganger!
第五个翻版!

390
00:20:23,220 --> 00:20:24,760
Uh,Lily?
嗯 Lily?

391
00:20:24,790 --> 00:20:27,710
- That dude looks noth... - Guys...
- 那家伙一点儿都... - 伙计们...

392
00:20:27,750 --> 00:20:29,240
Go with it.
将错就错了

393
00:20:29,260 --> 00:20:32,940
Kids,you can ask the universe for signs all you want...
孩子们 你可以向主寻求启示...

394
00:20:32,970 --> 00:20:35,430
- It's uncanny. - Right?
- 太诡异了 - 是吧?

395
00:20:35,450 --> 00:20:36,400
Just like Barney.
跟Barney一模一样

396
00:20:36,430 --> 00:20:37,220
Amazing.
太神奇了

397
00:20:37,250 --> 00:20:39,310
It's like looking in the mirror.
像在照镜子一样

398
00:20:39,340 --> 00:20:45,400
But ultimately,we only see what we want to see when we're ready to see it.
但是最终 时机成熟之后 我们只看得到希望看到的东西

399
00:20:45,430 --> 00:20:48,440
So,um,does this mean...?
也就是说...?

400
00:20:48,470 --> 00:20:50,500
Marshall Eriksen...
Marshall Eriksen...

401
00:20:50,540 --> 00:20:53,110
put a baby in my belly.
我们生个孩子吧

